window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Books 1-3 in the hit Chrysalis Monster-Evolution LitRPG series are now available in this special bundle, filled with action, laughs, and army-building to the extreme!</b></p> <p>Anthony has been reborn!</p> <p>Placed into the remarkable game-like world of Pangera.</p> <p>But something seems a little off... What's with these skills? <i>Bite</i>? <i>Dig</i>?</p> <p>Wait.... </p> <p>He's been reborn as a WHAT?! </p> <p>Follow Anthony as he attempts to adjust to his new life as an ant in his new Dungeon home. He'll have to learn how to survive, level-up, and grow both himself and his bite-sized colony into a force to be reckoned with.</p> <p><b><i>About this Series: </i></b>Jump into a rebirth story that mixes LitRPG and GameLit Elements with Monster Evolution, Levels, Stats, Skills, Magic, Power Progression, Kingdom Building, Party Building, Army Building, evolution, a monster MC, gigantic enemies (compared to Ant at least), and plenty of humor fitting for such a ludicrous premise.</p>"; 
